    {
      "beat_id": "B07",
      "t_start": 60,
      "estimated_duration_s": 13,
      "narration_text": "The Rayleigh\u2013Jeans curve rises forever \u2014 infinite energy at short wavelengths. The Planck curve peaks and falls. The two agree at long wavelengths, where packets are cheap, and diverge at short wavelengths, where the classical picture has no floor.",
